Abe et al. (2005), 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF206A9FF91792D91921BFAB" box="[1771,1825,1152,1177]" country="Japan" name="Fukui" pageId="219" pageNumber="981">Fukui</collectingRegion>
et al. (2015), Funakoshi (1991), Harada &amp; Yoshida (1978), Horaéek &amp; Hanak (1984), Jo Yeong-Seok et al. (2018), Kawai et al. (2003), Ohdachi et al. (2009), Ono &amp; Obara (1994), Park Su-Gon et al. (2015), Puechmaille, Allegrini et al. (2012), Smith &amp; Xie Yan (2008), Tsytsulina (2008f), Yamasaki (2004), Yoon Myung-Hee (1990), Yoshiyuki (1989).
</paragraph>
